{
  "id": "63440229fb203a001f8ad717",
  "title": "皮肉過程理論",
  "created": 1665401387,
  "updated": 1665447766,
  "lines": [
    {
      "id": "63440229fb203a001f8ad717",
      "text": "皮肉過程理論",
      "userId": "62a91a7a083437001de60035",
      "created": 1665401387,
      "updated": 1665401387
    },
    {
      "id": "6344022be6003500004a7922",
      "text": "「何かを考えないように努力すればするほど、かえってそのことが頭から離れなくなる」という現象を説明する理論",
      "userId": "62a91a7a083437001de60035",
      "created": 1665401387,
      "updated": 1665401388
    },
    {
      "id": "6344022ce6003500004a7923",
      "text": " [Ironic process theory]",
      "userId": "62a91a7a083437001de60035",
      "created": 1665401388,
      "updated": 1665401388
    },
    {
      "id": "6344022ce6003500004a7924",
      "text": " 1987年に[ダニエル・ウェグナー]([Daniel Merton Wegner])が以下の「[シロクマ実験]」の説明のために提唱した",
      "userId": "62a91a7a083437001de60035",
      "created": 1665401388,
      "updated": 1665401388
    },
    {
      "id": "6344022ce6003500004a7925",
      "text": "",
      "userId": "62a91a7a083437001de60035",
      "created": 1665401388,
      "updated": 1665401388
    },
    {
      "id": "6344022ce6003500004a7926",
      "text": "シロクマ実験",
      "userId": "62a91a7a083437001de60035",
      "created": 1665401388,
      "updated": 1665401388
    },
    {
      "id": "6344022ce6003500004a7927",
      "text": "　>A・B・Cの3つの実験参加者グループを用意する。",
      "userId": "62a91a7a083437001de60035",
      "created": 1665401388,
      "updated": 1665401388
    },
    {
      "id": "6344022ce6003500004a7928",
      "text": " >すべてのグループに[シロクマ]の1日を追った同じ映像を見せる。",
      "userId": "62a91a7a083437001de60035",
      "created": 1665401388,
      "updated": 1665401388
    },
    {
      "id": "6344022ce6003500004a7929",
      "text": " >Aグループの参加者には、シロクマのことを覚えておくように言う。",
      "userId": "62a91a7a083437001de60035",
      "created": 1665401388,
      "updated": 1665401388
    },
    {
      "id": "6344022ce6003500004a792a",
      "text": " >Bグループの参加者には、シロクマのことを考えても考えなくてもいいと言う。",
      "userId": "62a91a7a083437001de60035",
      "created": 1665401388,
      "updated": 1665401388
    },
    {
      "id": "6344022ce6003500004a792b",
      "text": " >Cグループの参加者には、[* シロクマのことだけは絶対に考えないでください]と言う。",
      "userId": "62a91a7a083437001de60035",
      "created": 1665401388,
      "updated": 1665401388
    },
    {
      "id": "6344022ce6003500004a792c",
      "text": " >一定の時間が経ったあと、実験協力者に映像について覚えているかを尋ねる。",
      "userId": "62a91a7a083437001de60035",
      "created": 1665401388,
      "updated": 1665401388
    },
    {
      "id": "6344022ce6003500004a792d",
      "text": ">この実験において、最も映像について詳しく覚えていたグループは「絶対に考えないで下さい」と言われたCグループであった。",
      "userId": "62a91a7a083437001de60035",
      "created": 1665401388,
      "updated": 1665401388
    },
    {
      "id": "6344022ce6003500004a792e",
      "text": "[https://ja.wikipedia.org/wiki/皮肉過程理論 皮肉過程理論 - Wikipedia]",
      "userId": "62a91a7a083437001de60035",
      "created": 1665401388,
      "updated": 1665401388
    },
    {
      "id": "6344022ce6003500004a792f",
      "text": "[https://2.bp.blogspot.com/-YAbY3TgxDlc/V4R0Z18Ul0I/AAAAAAAA8Mo/lPeqI5b8CrgRGcJnh2swxJtVK0NXEy8-ACLcB/s800/animal_bear_hokkyoku.png https://www.irasutoya.com/2016/07/blog-post_626.html]",
      "userId": "62a91a7a083437001de60035",
      "created": 1665401388,
      "updated": 1665401388
    },
    {
      "id": "6344022ce6003500004a7930",
      "text": ">[北極圏]に生息する体の白い大きな熊、[ホッキョクグマ]（シロクマ）のイラストです。",
      "userId": "62a91a7a083437001de60035",
      "created": 1665401388,
      "updated": 1665401388
    },
    {
      "id": "6344022ce6003500004a7931",
      "text": "　[北極熊]、[白熊]",
      "userId": "62a91a7a083437001de60035",
      "created": 1665401388,
      "updated": 1665401388
    },
    {
      "id": "6344022ce6003500004a7932",
      "text": "",
      "userId": "62a91a7a083437001de60035",
      "created": 1665401388,
      "updated": 1665401388
    },
    {
      "id": "6344022ce6003500004a7933",
      "text": "皮肉過程によって生じる、ありがちなパターン",
      "userId": "62a91a7a083437001de60035",
      "created": 1665401388,
      "updated": 1665401388
    },
    {
      "id": "6344022ce6003500004a7934",
      "text": "　絶対に○○！と意気込む→そのことばかり考えてしまう→○○に失敗する",
      "userId": "62a91a7a083437001de60035",
      "created": 1665401388,
      "updated": 1665401388
    },
    {
      "id": "6344022ce6003500004a7935",
      "text": "　○○に入る日常的行為の例",
      "userId": "62a91a7a083437001de60035",
      "created": 1665401388,
      "updated": 1665401388
    },
    {
      "id": "6344022ce6003500004a7936",
      "text": "　　[タバコ]を吸わない",
      "userId": "62a91a7a083437001de60035",
      "created": 1665401388,
      "updated": 1665401388
    },
    {
      "id": "6344022ce6003500004a7937",
      "text": "　　[酒]を飲まない",
      "userId": "62a91a7a083437001de60035",
      "created": 1665401388,
      "updated": 1665401388
    },
    {
      "id": "6344022ce6003500004a7938",
      "text": "　　[パチンコ]([ギャンブル])に行かない",
      "userId": "62a91a7a083437001de60035",
      "created": 1665401388,
      "updated": 1665401388
    },
    {
      "id": "6344022ce6003500004a7939",
      "text": "　　[ガチャ]に[課金]しない",
      "userId": "62a91a7a083437001de60035",
      "created": 1665401388,
      "updated": 1665401388
    },
    {
      "id": "6344022ce6003500004a793a",
      "text": "　　(笑うべきではない状況で)笑わない",
      "userId": "62a91a7a083437001de60035",
      "created": 1665401388,
      "updated": 1665401388
    },
    {
      "id": "6344022ce6003500004a793b",
      "text": "　　(人前で)緊張しない",
      "userId": "62a91a7a083437001de60035",
      "created": 1665401388,
      "updated": 1665401388
    },
    {
      "id": "6344022ce6003500004a793c",
      "text": "　　etc.",
      "userId": "62a91a7a083437001de60035",
      "created": 1665401388,
      "updated": 1665401388
    },
    {
      "id": "6344022ce6003500004a793d",
      "text": "上のパターンをまとめると「○○しないぞ！」と強く考えてしまうとそれに失敗しがち、ということ？",
      "userId": "62a91a7a083437001de60035",
      "created": 1665401388,
      "updated": 1665401388
    },
    {
      "id": "6344022ce6003500004a793e",
      "text": " 実際に失敗するかはさておき、何らかのエラーを招きうることは正しそう",
      "userId": "62a91a7a083437001de60035",
      "created": 1665401388,
      "updated": 1665401388
    },
    {
      "id": "6344022ce6003500004a793f",
      "text": "  ここで三振したらゲームセット＝絶対に三振してはいけない、という状況で手元が狂うとか",
      "userId": "62a91a7a083437001de60035",
      "created": 1665401388,
      "updated": 1665401388
    },
    {
      "id": "6344022ce6003500004a7940",
      "text": " 　 ↑これに関連して面白そうな論文があった[hatori.icon]",
      "userId": "62a91a7a083437001de60035",
      "created": 1665401388,
      "updated": 1665401388
    },
    {
      "id": "6344022ce6003500004a7941",
      "text": "　  [https://www.jstage.jst.go.jp/article/jjspopsy/advpub/0/advpub_2018-1803/_pdf 田中美吏, 柄木田健太, 運動パフォーマンスへの皮肉過程理論の援用 ―皮肉エラーと過補償エラーの実証とメカニズム―, スポーツ心理学研究　advpub_2018-1803]",
      "userId": "62a91a7a083437001de60035",
      "created": 1665401388,
      "updated": 1665401388
    },
    {
      "id": "6344022ce6003500004a7942",
      "text": " 「[考えたら負け]」とはちょっと意味が違う",
      "userId": "62a91a7a083437001de60035",
      "created": 1665401388,
      "updated": 1665401388
    },
    {
      "id": "6344022ce6003500004a7943",
      "text": "[皮肉過程理論#6344022ce6003500004a7935]",
      "userId": "5a4873ab2e26fb001479d3a9",
      "created": 1665401388,
      "updated": 1665434544
    },
    {
      "id": "634483ae79d3a90000a13cb2",
      "text": " ニ種類ありそうだと思った[sta.icon]",
      "userId": "5a4873ab2e26fb001479d3a9",
      "created": 1665434544,
      "updated": 1665434544
    },
    {
      "id": "634483ae79d3a90000a13cb3",
      "text": " \t1: 対象Aに関する欲求が強くて、ついやっちゃう系（お酒タバコギャンブルetc）",
      "userId": "5a4873ab2e26fb001479d3a9",
      "created": 1665434544,
      "updated": 1665434544
    },
    {
      "id": "634483ae79d3a90000a13cb4",
      "text": " \t2: 特定シチュエーションのときにAを思い出して適切に発揮する系（笑わない、緊張しないetc）",
      "userId": "5a4873ab2e26fb001479d3a9",
      "created": 1665434544,
      "updated": 1665434544
    },
    {
      "id": "634483ae79d3a90000a13cb5",
      "text": "",
      "userId": "5a4873ab2e26fb001479d3a9",
      "created": 1665434544,
      "updated": 1665434544
    },
    {
      "id": "6344022ce6003500004a7944",
      "text": "皮肉過程理論と以下のような心理状態との間に、何か関係はあるんだろうか？[hatori.icon]",
      "userId": "62a91a7a083437001de60035",
      "created": 1665401388,
      "updated": 1665401388
    },
    {
      "id": "6344022ce6003500004a7945",
      "text": "　禁止されると欲求が高まる",
      "userId": "62a91a7a083437001de60035",
      "created": 1665401388,
      "updated": 1665401388
    },
    {
      "id": "6344022ce6003500004a7946",
      "text": "　命令されると反抗したくなる",
      "userId": "62a91a7a083437001de60035",
      "created": 1665401388,
      "updated": 1665401388
    },
    {
      "id": "6344022ce6003500004a7947",
      "text": "",
      "userId": "62a91a7a083437001de60035",
      "created": 1665401388,
      "updated": 1665401388
    },
    {
      "id": "634482a979d3a90000a13caa",
      "text": "「しない」の難しさ？[sta.icon]",
      "userId": "5a4873ab2e26fb001479d3a9",
      "created": 1665434283,
      "updated": 1665434634
    },
    {
      "id": "634483f379d3a90000a13cb8",
      "text": " しないためには考えて自制する必要がある。難しい",
      "userId": "5a4873ab2e26fb001479d3a9",
      "created": 1665434613,
      "updated": 1665434648
    },
    {
      "id": "6344841579d3a90000a13cbc",
      "text": " \tなんだっけな、何か掲げるときは肯定形で表現しろ、みたいことはよく聞く",
      "userId": "5a4873ab2e26fb001479d3a9",
      "created": 1665434648,
      "updated": 1665434672
    },
    {
      "id": "634483fc79d3a90000a13cb9",
      "text": " 何回もやっちゃう",
      "userId": "5a4873ab2e26fb001479d3a9",
      "created": 1665434622,
      "updated": 1665434625
    },
    {
      "id": "6344840279d3a90000a13cba",
      "text": " その過程で定着してしまう？",
      "userId": "5a4873ab2e26fb001479d3a9",
      "created": 1665434628,
      "updated": 1665434632
    },
    {
      "id": "6344839379d3a90000a13cb1",
      "text": "",
      "userId": "5a4873ab2e26fb001479d3a9",
      "created": 1665434517,
      "updated": 1665434517
    },
    {
      "id": "634482a879d3a90000a13ca9",
      "text": "",
      "userId": "5a4873ab2e26fb001479d3a9",
      "created": 1665434283,
      "updated": 1665434283
    },
    {
      "id": "6344022ce6003500004a7948",
      "text": "関連項目",
      "userId": "62a91a7a083437001de60035",
      "created": 1665401388,
      "updated": 1665401388
    },
    {
      "id": "6344022ce6003500004a7949",
      "text": "　[ザ・ゲーム]",
      "userId": "62a91a7a083437001de60035",
      "created": 1665401388,
      "updated": 1665401388
    },
    {
      "id": "6344022ce6003500004a794a",
      "text": "　[パラドックス]",
      "userId": "62a91a7a083437001de60035",
      "created": 1665401388,
      "updated": 1665401388
    },
    {
      "id": "6344022ce6003500004a794b",
      "text": " [ストライサンド効果]",
      "userId": "62a91a7a083437001de60035",
      "created": 1665401388,
      "updated": 1665401388
    },
    {
      "id": "6344022ce6003500004a794c",
      "text": " [カリギュラ効果]",
      "userId": "62a91a7a083437001de60035",
      "created": 1665401388,
      "updated": 1665401388
    },
    {
      "id": "6344022ce6003500004a794d",
      "text": "　[タブー]",
      "userId": "62a91a7a083437001de60035",
      "created": 1665401388,
      "updated": 1665401388
    },
    {
      "id": "6344022ce6003500004a794e",
      "text": "　[見るなのタブー]",
      "userId": "5ae7fecf7766b7001455cbd3",
      "created": 1665401388,
      "updated": 1665447766
    },
    {
      "id": "6344022ce6003500004a794f",
      "text": "",
      "userId": "62a91a7a083437001de60035",
      "created": 1665401388,
      "updated": 1665401388
    },
    {
      "id": "6344022ce6003500004a7950",
      "text": "皮肉過程理論と(間接的には)関連がありそうなもの",
      "userId": "62a91a7a083437001de60035",
      "created": 1665401388,
      "updated": 1665401388
    },
    {
      "id": "6344022ce6003500004a7951",
      "text": "（これらは[伏線]というかお決まりのパターンの意味での「[フラグ]」と言った方がいいかもしれない）",
      "userId": "62a91a7a083437001de60035",
      "created": 1665401388,
      "updated": 1665401388
    },
    {
      "id": "6344022ce6003500004a7952",
      "text": "　[即堕ち2コマシリーズ]",
      "userId": "62a91a7a083437001de60035",
      "created": 1665401388,
      "updated": 1665401388
    },
    {
      "id": "6344022ce6003500004a7953",
      "text": "　　｢絶対XXXなんかに負けたりしない！｣ｷﾘｯ　→　  ｢XXXには勝てなかったよ…｣",
      "userId": "62a91a7a083437001de60035",
      "created": 1665401388,
      "updated": 1665401388
    },
    {
      "id": "6344022ce6003500004a7954",
      "text": "　　[https://dic.pixiv.net/a/即堕ち2コマシリーズ 即堕ち2コマシリーズ (そくおちにこましりーず)とは【ピクシブ百科事典】]",
      "userId": "62a91a7a083437001de60035",
      "created": 1665401388,
      "updated": 1665401388
    },
    {
      "id": "6344022ce6003500004a7955",
      "text": "　　[https://dic.nicovideo.jp/a/即堕ち2コマシリーズ 即堕ち2コマシリーズとは (ソクオチニコマシリーズとは) 単語記事 - ニコニコ大百科]",
      "userId": "62a91a7a083437001de60035",
      "created": 1665401388,
      "updated": 1665401388
    },
    {
      "id": "6344022ce6003500004a7956",
      "text": "　「[押すなよ！絶対に押すなよ！]」→　押す",
      "userId": "62a91a7a083437001de60035",
      "created": 1665401388,
      "updated": 1665401388
    },
    {
      "id": "6344022ce6003500004a7957",
      "text": "　 [https://dic.pixiv.net/a/押すなよ!絶対に押すなよ! 押すなよ!絶対に押すなよ! (おすなよぜったいにおすなよ)とは【ピクシブ百科事典】]",
      "userId": "62a91a7a083437001de60035",
      "created": 1665401388,
      "updated": 1665401388
    },
    {
      "id": "6344022ce6003500004a7958",
      "text": "  [https://dic.nicovideo.jp/a/絶対に押すなよ 絶対に押すなよとは (ゼッタイニオスナヨとは) 単語記事 - ニコニコ大百科]",
      "userId": "62a91a7a083437001de60035",
      "created": 1665401388,
      "updated": 1665401388
    },
    {
      "id": "6344022ce6003500004a7959",
      "text": " 「[エヴァにだけは乗らんでくださいよ！]」→　乗る",
      "userId": "62a91a7a083437001de60035",
